# Customer Service — http profile: localhost:5002 (veja Properties/launchSettings.json)
# Para testar pelo gateway, use o ficheiro na raiz: DevApi.http

@CustomerService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5002

@customerId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### GET todos
GET {{CustomerService_HostAddress}}/api/customers

### GET por id — substitua @customerId
GET {{CustomerService_HostAddress}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}

### GET por e-mail (%40 = @)
GET {{CustomerService_HostAddress}}/api/customers/email/cliente%40teste.com

### POST criar
POST {{CustomerService_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cliente Teste",
  "email": "cliente@teste.com",
  "phone": "+5511999999999",
  "documentNumber": "12345678901"
}

### PUT — substitua @customerId
PUT {{CustomerService_HostAddress}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cliente Atualizado",
  "email": "cliente@teste.com",
  "phone": "+5511888888888",
  "documentNumber": "12345678901"
}

### DELETE — substitua @customerId
DELETE {{CustomerService_HostAddress}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}
